# Code owners for the street framework.
#
# Owners are automatically requested for review on pull requests that touch
# matching paths. Combined with a branch-protection rule that requires an
# approving review before merge, this is what lets the OpenSSF Scorecard
# "Code-Review" check credit changes as reviewed.
#
# Format: <path pattern>  <owner(s)>

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                           @hassanmubiru

# Security-sensitive areas — keep an explicit owner so changes are always reviewed.
/.github/                   @hassanmubiru
/packages/core/src/security/    @hassanmubiru
/packages/core/src/database/    @hassanmubiru
/SECURITY.md                @hassanmubiru
